{"tid":2091840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際線] 美國參議院一致通過眾議院版本的《香港自治法案》","createTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T01:49:26.000Z","uid":86295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e851e2c544408146d99dc9b812fb8ba63cfc7e6","tid":2091840,"uid":86295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"繼《香港自治法案》昨日在美國眾議院一致通過後，綜合外電報道，美國參議院當地時間周四一致通過眾議院版本的《香港自治法案》，待美國特朗普簽署法案後便會生效。<br />\n<br />\n法案將制裁支持打壓香港自治的個人、企業、鎮壓示威的香港警察，以及推動「港區國安法」的中國官員將會受到懲處。另外，跟這些個人及企業有重大業務往來（significant transactions）的銀行或金融機構，都可能面對制裁；又會限制官員進行美元交易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%8F%8A%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%BE%85%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E5%BE%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25BE%2585%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2595%2588%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=cf9d3fb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%2589%2593%25E5